data.description: This upgraded 5-bedroom, 3-bath home is in a well-established neighborhood in the sought-after Mansfield ISD. This unique corner lot home is located in a sought-after neighborhood! A rare corner alongside a beautiful green space. The spacious floor plan has large open rooms throughout the home. There are two oversized living areas downstairs, one with a cozy fireplace. Featuring a fabulous kitchen with new stainless steel appliances, tons of cabinet and counter space, and is open to the living room area. The second story includes a vast master bedroom, a master bath with dual sinks, a large walk-in shower, and 4 additional bedrooms. Step outside to your beautiful double lot with a newly fenced backyard open to a lovely grassy area, ideal for outdoor activities. Step outdoors to the enormous backyard with a new fence surrounding the home.
